<!-- My Story Section -->
<section class="py-5 bg-light" id="my-story">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <div class="text-center mb-5">
                    <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">My Journey</h2>
                    <p class="lead text-muted">From Laboratory to Creative Studio</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="story-timeline">
                    <!-- Step 1: Education & Career -->
                    <div class="story-step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-book"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">The Academic Path</h3>
                            <p class="mb-3">
                                My journey began in the world of science. After completing my <strong>Master's in Food Science</strong>, 
                                I stepped into the food industry, working with various companies and gaining valuable experience 
                                in product development, quality control, and research.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-muted">
                                While I enjoyed the precision and methodology of science, something was always calling me back to my roots...
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 2: The Hobby -->
                    <div class="story-step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-heart"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">A Lifelong Passion</h3>
                            <p class="mb-3">
                                Throughout my career, <strong>handcrafts were always my escape</strong>. Whether it was intricate 
                                bangles, beautiful sarees, or delicate blouses, I spent every free moment creating. What started 
                                as a hobby soon became my sanctuary — a place where science met art, and precision met creativity.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-muted">
                                Friends and family loved my creations, often asking, "Why don't you sell these?" That question planted a seed...
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 3: The Leap -->
                    <div class="story-step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-rocket"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Taking the Leap</h3>
                            <p class="mb-3">
                                In 2024, I made a bold decision: to turn my passion into a business. <strong>Kavya's Creations was born</strong> — 
                                not just as a store, but as a celebration of handmade art, traditional craftsmanship, and the joy 
                                of creating something beautiful with your own hands.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-muted">
                                Every piece you see here is crafted with the same attention to detail I learned in the lab, 
                                combined with the love and creativity I've nurtured all my life.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 4: Today -->
                    <div class="story-step">
                        <div class="step-icon">
                            <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Today & Beyond</h3>
                            <p class="mb-3">
                                Today, I wake up every day excited to create. Each bangle, saree, and blouse tells a story — 
                                mine and yours. My background in science taught me discipline, quality control, and perfection. 
                                My passion for handcrafts taught me patience, creativity, and the beauty of imperfection.
                            </p>
                            <div class="highlight-box">
                                <i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up text-primary"></i>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    <strong>My Promise:</strong> Every product is handcrafted by me with love, care, and attention 
                                    to detail. When you buy from Kavya's Creations, you're not just buying a product — 
                                    you're supporting a dream, preserving traditional art, and owning something truly unique.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

